results.name: The siteswap sequence (the deltas p[i]-i, i in ]-inf,+inf[, folded from Z to N, mapping 0->1, 1->2, -1->3, 2->4, -2->5, etc.) for A065278.
xref: The bisection of even terms (the positive half of Z) is given by A053644 and the bisection of odd terms (the nonpositive half of Z) is given by A065280.
